{"tid":2039533,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"美國call UN安理會篇文承認香港人存在","createTime":"2020-05-28T05:36:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-30T00:59:54.000Z","uid":65764,"like":326,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":56,"replies":[{"pid":"5b92c01c260a9af777ea0f1fc3d7773521ef95e8","tid":2039533,"uid":65764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T05:36:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://usun.usmission.gov/call-for-un-security-council-meeting-on-hong-kong/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fusun.usmission.gov%2Fcall-for-un-security-council-meeting-on-hong-kong%2F&d=%2FAUJPsyZ5YTgQdLV7Kr5PhyAur%2Bbp9MVyOkMM5%2FMxDY%3D&h=3edf6728\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://usun.usmission.gov/call-for-un-security-council-meeting-on-hong-kong/</a><br />\n<br />\nCall for UN Security Council Meeting on Hong Kong<br />\n<br />\nU.S. MISSION TO THE UNITED NATIONS<br />\nNew York, New York<br />\nMay 27, 2020<br />\n<br />\nCall for UN Security Council Meeting on Hong Kong<br />\n<br />\nThe United States is deeply concerned by actions taken by the People&rsquo;s Republic of China (PRC) National People&rsquo;s Congress that fundamentally undermine Hong Kong&rsquo;s high degree of autonomy and freedoms as guaranteed under the Sino-British Joint Declaration of 1984, which was registered with the UN as a legally binding treaty, and the Basic Law. This is a matter of urgent global concern that implicates international peace and security, and warrants the immediate attention of the UN Security Council.<br />\n<br />\nAs a result, the United States called today for a virtual meeting of the Security Council to discuss these acts and the PRC&rsquo;s proposed national security law that would threaten Hong Kong&rsquo;s democratic institutions and civil liberties. Such actions confirm the PRC&rsquo;s contempt and complete disregard for its international obligations.<br />\n<br />\nUnsurprisingly, the PRC has refused to allow this virtual meeting to proceed in the Security Council. This is another example of the Chinese Communist Party&rsquo;s fear of transparency and international accountability for its actions, and belief that it can exploit the current global health pandemic to distract the world from its intended assault on Hong Kong and abrogation of its own commitments to <strong>the Hong Kong people</strong>.<br />\n<br />\nThis action, coupled with the PRC&rsquo;s gross cover-up and mismanagement of the COVID-19 crisis, its constant violations of its international human rights commitments, and its unlawful behavior in the South China Sea, should make obvious to all that Beijing is not behaving as a responsible UN member state.<br />\n<br />\nWe call on the PRC to immediately reverse course and honor its promises under the Sino-British Joint Declaration.<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔知大家有冇留意，美國國務卿 Mike Pompeo 近排不斷講「香港人」？今朝佢除咗cert咗香港冇自治之外，原來美國直情想將香港問題放上聯合國安全理事會議程。但因為武漢肺炎暫停會議，要開視像會議又要中國同意，所以提唔到。後來嘅聲明又有講「香港人」。一個國家大張旗鼓咁講「香港人」呢個做法其實係好唔簡單，因為呢種事實認定會帶來國際法民族自決權利嘅法律後果。例如西藏就有3份聯合國大會決議提及「藏人」。"},{"pid":"913560023f22fd634f5d98913cc8fd5bc600f0cf","tid":2039533,"uid":338439,"like":76,"dislike":1,"score":75,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T05:36:55.000Z","msg":"Sir this way, 我哋要建立自己嘅民族"},{"pid":"3fd1367d816bffea7480f81e815ef425b824435b","tid":2039533,"uid":124711,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T05:38:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a20cc02e88f92006d78f099e7fdf1cf100313a0a","tid":2039533,"uid":107297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T05:42:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=