By":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T15:33:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T15:43:22.000Z","msg":"如果你係香港出世你最好小心啲，叛國好嚴重。中國移民就死開。"},{"pid":"1b9ad0504a84e1483c2a92bf813184185cf99d01","tid":2039533,"uid":99420,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T15:44:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"28612e49c06a11e67c22bc8816b82d0ee08dc501","tid":2039533,"uid":251366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T15:47:39.000Z","msg":"聯合國係咪欠左我地一個公道 點解其他殖民地可以有權自決我地唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e66c3bf85bd1d2623ae11d6ac373c87129b5a292","tid":2039533,"uid":168267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"81b1c262d9676fe04d507b65c6f177110e71d584","tid":2039533,"uid":118120,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T06:24:59.000Z","msg":"係時候諗下香港人既正式英文係點叫<br />\nHong Konger ? HongKongese ?<br />\n你想人地承認你, 你都要有個正式英文俾人叫到"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T15:59:31.000Z","msg":"我係Hongkonger派<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n'Hongkonger' makes it to world stage with place in the Oxford English Dictionary <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.scmp.com/news/hong-kong/article/1451929/finally-hongkonger-arrives-world-stage\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scmp.com%2Fnews%2Fhong-kong%2Farticle%2F1451929%2Ffinally-hongkonger-arrives-world-stage&d=%2FAUJPsyZ5YTgQdLV7Kr5PhyAur%2Bbp9MVyOkMM5%2FMxDY%3D&h=70458e17\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.scmp.com/news/hong-kong/article/1451929/finally-hongkonger-arrives-world-stage</a>"}],"pinned":{"pid":"737e2dfccc4adb476190f23c81958c36f7c8f62a","tid":2039533,"uid":65764,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T00:59:54.000Z","msg":"今日侵侵仲話 unique Hong Kong identity <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}}